<h2 id="what-is-liondesk">🦁 What Is LionDesk?</h2>

LionDesk entered the market in 2015 with a singular focus: giving real estate professionals an affordable, easy-to-learn CRM. The platform has maintained that positioning while adding video messaging, AI lead follow-up, and power dialer capabilities.

Where GoHighLevel aims to replace your entire stack, LionDesk embraces integration. The platform connects natively with over 250 real estate tools including major lead sources like Zillow, Realtor.com, and Facebook Lead Ads. LionDesk's transaction management integrates with Dotloop, SkySlope, and other closing platforms.

The 2026 release brought significant AI improvements to LionDesk's Gabby assistant, which now handles initial lead qualification conversations with impressive accuracy. The platform also added enhanced video texting capabilities and improved drip campaign analytics.

